'''靛蓝航空'''（{{lang-en|'''IndiGo'''}}）是一家[[印度|印度]]的航空公司，总部位于[[古尔冈|古尔冈]]。靛蓝航空于2006年首航以来，一直运营单一机型（[[空中客车A320|空中客车A320]]）的机队，提供全经济舱座位布局。截至2016年2月，靛蓝航空是印度运载乘客人数最高的航空公司，市场份额达到36.8%，在亚洲[[低成本航空公司|低成本航空公司]]中规模仅次于[[印尼狮航|印尼狮航]]。靛蓝航空拥有40个航点，主要枢纽机场为[[德里|德里]][[英迪拉·甘地国际机场|英迪拉·甘地国际机场]]。

==历史==

靛蓝航空由旅居[[美国|美国]]的[[海外印度人|海外印度人]]{{link-en|拉凯什·甘瓦尔|Rakesh Gangwal}}和英谷集团（{{lang-en|InterGlobe Enterprises}}）的{{link-en|拉胡尔·巴蒂亚|Rahul Bhatia}}共同创立<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cnbc.com/2015/06/30/interglobe-aviation-owner-of-indias-indigo-airline-files-for-ipo.html|title=Owner of India's biggest airline files for IPO|date=2015-06-30|work=CNBC|access-date=2016-03-16}}</ref>。英谷集团持有51.12%股权，甘瓦尔通过注册于美国的公司持有47.88%股权<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/indigo-gives-handsome-payback-to-promoters-113111500988_1.html|title=IndiGo gives handsome payback to promoters|date=2013-11-16|first=Anees|last=Padnis|newspaper=Business Standard|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328193722/http://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/indigo-gives-handsome-payback-to-promoters-113111500988_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=FIPB approves proposal to convert Rakesh Gangwal's IndiGo stake to NRI category|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2014-08-02/news/52356509_1_fipb-foreign-investment-promotion-board-equity-shares|newspaper=The Economic Times|date=2014-10-02|access-date=2016-03-16}}</ref>。2005年6月，靛蓝航空订购了100架[[空中客车A320-200|空中客车A320-200]]型客机<ref name="order">{{cite news|title=IndiGo Airlines to fly soon|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2005-06-22/news/27477022_1_lease-planes-aircraft-airbus-industrie|newspaper=The Economic Times|date=2005-06-22|access-date=2016-03-16}}</ref>。2006年7月28日，靛蓝航空接收了第一架飞机<ref name="1st" /><ref name="1st2">{{cite news|title=IndiGo takes delivery of its first brand new Airbus A320 aircraft|url=http://www.thehindu.com/thehindu/holnus/006200607290310.htm|archive-url=http://www.aviationindia.net/2006/07/indigo-takes-delivery-of-its-first.html|newspaper=[[印度教徒报|The Hindu]]|date=2006-07-29|archive-date=2006-07-29|access-date=2012-02-16}}</ref>，随后于2006年8月4日开始运营，第一条航线为[[英迪拉·甘地国际机场|德里]]经[[古瓦哈提|古瓦哈提]]前往[[因帕尔|因帕尔]]<ref name=take-off>{{cite news|title=Indigo's first flight to take-off on Aug 4|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2006-07-13/news/27459427_1_first-flight-interglobe-president-bruce-ashby|newspaper=The Economic Times|date=2006-07-13|access-date=2016-03-16}}</ref>。到2006年底，靛蓝航空机队包括6架飞机；2007年，又增加了9架飞机<ref name=take-off/>。2010年12月，靛蓝航空的规模超过[[印度航空|印度航空]]，成为印度第三大航空公司，市场份额达到17.3%，仅次于[[翠鸟航空|翠鸟航空]]和[[捷特航空|捷特航空]]<ref>{{cite news|title=IndiGo pips Air India to become No. 3 airline|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/indigo-pips-ai-to-become-no.-3-airline/727160/|newspaper=[[印度快报|Indian Express]]|date=2010-12-21|access-date=2016-03-16|archive-date=2011-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110123222901/http://www.indianexpress.com/news/indigo-pips-ai-to-become-no.-3-airline/727160|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年，靛蓝航空订购了180架空中客车A320飞机，价值150亿美元<ref>{{cite news|title=IndiGo airline picks up 180 jets|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2011-01-13/news/28428535_1_airbus-aircraft-rahul-bhatia-airbus-a320s|newspaper=The Economic Times|date=2011-01-13|access-date=2016-03-16}}</ref>。2011年1月，经过五年运营后，靛蓝航空获得经营国际航线的许可<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.rediff.com/business/report/indigo-gets-govt-nod-to-launch-international-operations/20110119.htm|title=IndiGo gets govt nod to launch international operations|work=Rediff|date=2011-01-11|access-date=2016-03-13|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422140045/http://www.rediff.com/business/report/indigo-gets-govt-nod-to-launch-international-operations/20110119.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年9月，靛蓝航空開始營運国际航线<ref name=dubai>{{cite news|title=IndiGo to launch international flights from Sept. 1|first=Vinay|last=Kumar|url=http://www.thehindu.com/business/companies/indigo-to-launch-international-flights-from-sept-1/article2104373.ece|newspaper=[[印度教徒报|The Hindu]]|date=2011-06-14|access-date=2012-02-22|archive-date=2018-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303131336/http://www.thehindu.com/business/companies/indigo-to-launch-international-flights-from-sept-1/article2104373.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年12月，{{link-en|印度民航总局|Directorate General of Civil Aviation (India)}}称，包括靛蓝航空在内的多家航空公司受到财政问题影响，违反了强制收集关键飞行安全数据的要求<ref>{{cite news|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/indigo-spicejet-goair-jet-airways-airlines-flout-norms-dgca/1/167838.html|title=IndiGo, SpiceJet airlines violate mandatory safety norms: DGCA|newspaper=India Today|date=2012-01-09|access-date=2012-07-13|archive-date=2012-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311183607/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/indigo-spicejet-goair-jet-airways-airlines-flout-norms-dgca/1/167838.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年2月，靛蓝航空接收了第50架飞机，此时距其开始运营尚不满六年<ref name="50th">{{cite news|title=IndiGo gets delivery of its 50th Airbus A-320 aircraft|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2012-02-10/news/31046344_1_indigo-president-aditya-ghosh-new-flights-airbus-aircraft|newspaper=The Economic Times|date=2012-02-10|access-date=2016-03-16}}</ref>。2012年第一季度，靛蓝航空是印度盈利状况最佳的航空公司，同时以客运市场规模计算，靛蓝航空已成为印度第二大航空公司<ref name="compare">{{Cite news|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/a-tale-of-two-airlines-kingfisher-vs-indigo-112022100014_1.html|title=A tale of two airlines: Kingfisher vs IndiGo|first=Mihir|last=Mishra|newspaper=Business Standard|date=2012-02-21|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329115312/http://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/a-tale-of-two-airlines-kingfisher-vs-indigo-112022100014_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年8月17日，靛蓝航空开始运营刚满六年，客运市场规模超过捷特航空，成为印度第一大航空公司<ref name="bigair">{{cite news|title=IndiGo flies past Jet to become largest airline|url=http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/indigo-flies-past-jet-to-become-largest-airline/483595/|newspaper=Business Standard|date=2012-08-18|access-date=2012-08-18|archive-date=2012-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120819003446/http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/indigo-flies-past-jet-to-become-largest-airline/483595/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年1月，靛蓝航空是亚洲成长第二快的[[低成本航空公司|低成本航空公司]]，仅次于[[印尼狮航|印尼狮航]]<ref name="fastair">{{cite web|title=IndiGo among the fastest expanding airlines globally|url=http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/indigo-amongfastest-expanding-airlines-globally/497496/|newspaper=Business Standard|date=2013-01-02|access-date=2013-01-11|archive-date=2013-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130104094637/http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/indigo-amongfastest-expanding-airlines-globally/497496/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年2月，{{link-en|印度民用航空局|Ministry of Civil Aviation (India)}}限制靛蓝航空当年只能接收5架飞机，靛蓝航空因此寻求设立子公司经营低成本区域航线。稍后，靛蓝航空宣布其计划向局方申请当年额外引进4架飞机，全年共9架<ref>{{cite news|title=IndiGo to set up regional airline to tap small towns|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2013-02-13/news/37079404_1_indigo-president-aditya-ghosh-indigo-plans-rahul-bhatia|newspaper=The Economic Times|date=2013-02-13|access-date=2013-02-14}}</ref>。截至2014年3月，靛蓝航空成为以座位数计的亚洲第二大航空公司<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://www.uatp.com/files/uploads/PDF/AD2014PPT_CAPA.pdf|title=Analyst Viewpoint: Asian airline industry overview|first=Brent|last=Sobhie|publisher=CAPA|format=PDF|page=35|access-date=2016-06-01|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417145212/http://uatp.com/files/uploads/PDF/AD2014PPT_CAPA.pdf|archivedate=2015-04-17}}</ref>。

2015年8月，靛蓝航空订购了250架[[空中客车A320neo系列|空中客车A320neo系列]]飞机，价值270亿美元，以订购飞机数量计算，这在当时是空中客车历史上最大的单笔订单<ref name="largestab" /><ref name="largestit">{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/IndiGo-orders-250-planes-for-27bn/articleshow/48519687.cms|title=IndiGo orders 250 planes|newspaper=[[Times_of_India|Times of India]]|date=2015-08-18|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328113422/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/IndiGo-orders-250-planes-for-27bn/articleshow/48519687.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年10月19日，靛蓝航空宣布了募集{{INRConvert|3200|c}}的[[首次公开募股|首次公开募股]]计划，第一个交易日定于10月27日<ref>{{cite news|title=IndiGo Airlines IPO to open on October 27, price band Rs 700-765|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/ipos/fpos/indigo-airlines-ipo-to-open-on-tuesday-price-band-rs-700-765/articleshow/49453526.cms|newspaper=The Economic Times|date=2015-10-20|access-date=2016-06-05|archive-date=2015-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151029054406/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/ipos/fpos/indigo-airlines-ipo-to-open-on-tuesday-price-band-rs-700-765/articleshow/49453526.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2016年2月，靛蓝航空是印度运载乘客人数最高的航空公司，市场份额达到36.8%<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/india-s-domestic-passenger-demand-up-25-percent-iata-116040700595_1.html|title=India's domestic passenger demand up 25 percent: IATA|newspaper=Business Standard|date=2014-04-06|access-date=2016-04-14|archive-date=2016-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423143800/http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/india-s-domestic-passenger-demand-up-25-percent-iata-116040700595_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年10月，靛蓝航空订购了300架[[空中客车A320neo系列|空中客车A320neo系列]]飞机，价值330亿美元，打破了由她自己所創的空中客车最大訂單紀錄。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://onemileatatime.com/indigo-airbus-order/|title=IndiGo Orders Further 300 A320neo Aircraft|work=One Mile at a Home|date=31 October 2019}}</ref><ref name="IndiGo 300 A320N">{{cite web |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/indigo-orders-300-a320-neo-family-planes-worth-rs-2-4-lakh-crore-to-get-730-planed-at-rate-of-one-a-week-for-next-12-years/articleshow/71809801.cms|title=IndiGo gives Rs 2.4 lakh crore order for 300 A320 Neo aircraft |work=Times of India |date=31 October 2019}}</ref>

==运营==

靛蓝航空总部位于[[印度|印度]][[古尔冈|古尔冈]]<ref name="headq"/>。靛蓝航空是印度发展最快、规模最大的有盈利的航空公司<ref name="fastair"/>。靛蓝航空的成功可归功于其独特的、可有效控制成本的商业模式<ref name="compare"/>。靛蓝航空运营单一机型（空中客车A320）的机队，提供相似的全经济舱座位布局，可以降低機組人员训练和飛機维护成本。通过大批量的采购，可以降低每架飞机的单价。靛蓝航空还致力于降低[[机场地勤|周转时间]]至20分钟，使得每架飞机日均飞行时间达到12小时，提升了飞机使用率。靛蓝航空的职员可能同时身兼数职，例如值机人员可能同时也是行李操作员<ref name="turn">{{Cite news|url=http://www.businesstoday.in/magazine/features/indigo-operations-in-pictures/story/185133.html|title=Soaring above the rest|first=Vivan|last=Mehta|date=2012-06-24|access-date=2016-03-19|newspaper=Business Today}}</ref>。

==航点==
{{main|靛蓝航空航点}}
截至2016年3月，靛蓝航空拥有40个航点，其中国内航点35个，国际航点5个<ref>{{cite news|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/airlines-/-aviation/airlines-to-operate-14869-flights-per-week-in-summer-schedule/articleshow/51457030.cms|title=Airlines to operate 14,869 flights per week in summer schedule|newspaper=The Economic Times|date=2016-03-18|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821234117/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/airlines-/-aviation/airlines-to-operate-14869-flights-per-week-in-summer-schedule/articleshow/51457030.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="daily flights">{{cite news|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/money/report-indigo-adds-8-new-daily-flights-2170806|title=IndiGo adds 8 new daily flights|newspaper=DNA|date=2016-01-27|access-date=2016-03-04|archive-date=2016-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131023922/http://www.dnaindia.com/money/report-indigo-adds-8-new-daily-flights-2170806|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="live Mint">{{cite news|url=http://www.livemint.com/Companies/RfU4n2VcHZ7ntCuxMOMnvN/IndiGosoarsaboveJetAirwaysAirIndia.html|title=IndiGo soars above Jet Airways, Air India|newspaper=Mint|date=2015-06-23|access-date=2015-06-27|archive-date=2015-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701235017/http://www.livemint.com/Companies/RfU4n2VcHZ7ntCuxMOMnvN/IndiGosoarsaboveJetAirwaysAirIndia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。靛蓝航空的枢纽机场为德里的英迪拉·甘地国际机场<ref>{{cite web|url=http://centreforaviation.com/profiles/airlines/indigo-6e|title=Profile on IndiGo|publisher=CAPA|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317092308/http://centreforaviation.com/profiles/airlines/indigo-6e|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年1月，靛蓝航空获得经营国际航线的许可<ref name=international>{{cite news|title=IndiGo Airlines to fly to Dubai, Bangkok, Singapore from September|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2011-06-14/news/29657072_1_indigo-president-aditya-ghosh-aircraft-cabin-crew|newspaper=The Economic Times|location=New Delhi |date=2011-06-14|access-date=2012-02-22}}</ref>，第一条国际航线为[[德里|德里]]往返[[迪拜国际机场|迪拜]]<ref name=dubai/>，稍后其国际航点又拓展至[[素万那普机场|曼谷]]、[[新加坡樟宜机场|新加坡]]、[[马斯喀特国际机场|马斯喀特]]和[[特里布万国际机场|加德满都]]<ref name=dubai/>。靛蓝航空还在考虑拓展[[昆明长水国际机场|昆明]]航点<ref>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kolkata/2nd-Kolkata-China-flight-on-cards/articleshow/47648761.cms|title=2nd Kolkata-China flight on cards|newspaper=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|date=2015-07-13|access-date=2015-07-21}}</ref>。

==机队==
