===机队信息===
靛蓝航空分别于2006年7月、2012年2月、2014年11月接收了其首架<ref name="1st">{{cite press release|url=http://www.airbus.com/newsevents/news-events-single/detail/indigo-celebrates-delivery-of-first-airbus-a320/|title=IndiGo celebrates delivery of first Airbus A320|work=Airbus|date=2006-07-28|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065007/http://www.airbus.com/newsevents/news-events-single/detail/indigo-celebrates-delivery-of-first-airbus-a320/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="1st2" />、第50架<ref name="50th"/>、第100架飞机<ref>{{cite news|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/airlines-/-aviation/indigo-gets-100th-aircraft-completing-its-first-order-of-many-airbus-a-32/articleshow/45037857.cms|title =IndiGo gets 100th aircraft completing its first order of many Airbus A-320|newspaper=The Economic Times|date=2014-11-04|access-date=2014-11-04}}</ref>。靛蓝航空原本计划2015年起开始接收2011年订购的空中客车A320neo系列飞机<ref>{{cite news|last=Sinha|first=Saurabh|title=Aircraft order is just a drop in ocean: IndiGo|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/Aircraft-order-is-just-a-drop-in-ocean-IndiGo/articleshow/7273266.cms|access-date=2011-01-13|newspaper=[[Times_of_India|Times of India]]|date=2011-01-13|archive-date=2011-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110117014257/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/Aircraft-order-is-just-a-drop-in-ocean-IndiGo/articleshow/7273266.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但是由于飞机制造上的延迟，实际到了2016年3月11日方才开始接收<ref name="airbus"/>。期间，靛蓝航空[[干租|干租]]了22架飞机以应对航線發展需求<ref name="Delay">{{cite news|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/airbus-group-interglobe-idUKL8N14A1YE20151221|title=Airbus delays A320neo delivery for Indian airline IndiGo|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2016-12-21|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326020539/http://uk.reuters.com/article/airbus-group-interglobe-idUKL8N14A1YE20151221|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===新飞机订购===
[[File:IGO_A320neo_F-WWII!6849_22dec15_LFBO.jpg|thumb]]一架待交付的靛蓝航空[[空中客车A320|空中客车A320]]]]

2005年6月[[巴黎国际航空航天展|巴黎国际航空航天展]]期间，靛蓝航空订购了第一批100架空中客车A320-200型飞机，价值60亿美元<ref name="order"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/4098906.stm|title=Airbus wins $6bn order from India|work=BBC News|date=2005-06-16|access-date=2010-08-30|archive-date=2012-07-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68s26AX4l?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/4098906.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.airbus.com/en/corporate/orders_and_deliveries|title=Airbus Orders and Deliveries|publisher=Airbus|access-date=2010-08-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68s273hze?url=http://www.airbus.com/company/history/|archivedate=2012-07-03}}</ref>。2011年1月11日，靛蓝航空作为空中客车A320neo系列的启动客户，签署了价值150亿美元的[[谅解备忘录|谅解备忘录]]，订购180架飞机，其中150架为neo系列<ref>{{Cite press release|title=IndiGo commits to 180 A320s, largest jet order in aviation history|publisher=Airbus|date=2011-11-01|url=http://www.airbus.com/presscentre/pressreleases/press-release-detail/detail/indigo-commits-to-180-a320s-largest-jet-order-in-aviation-history/4176/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110115081656/http://www.airbus.com/presscentre/pressreleases/press-release-detail/detail/indigo-commits-to-180-a320s-largest-jet-order-in-aviation-history/4176/|archive-date=2011-01-15|access-date=2011-01-14|work=Airbus|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name=BBC>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-13884433|title=Airbus and AirAsia announce record deal for 200 planes|work=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2011-06-23|access-date=2011-06-23|archive-date=2011-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623112044/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-13884433|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年10月15日，靛蓝航空表达了订购250架空中客车A320neo系列飞机的意向，目录价格达到257亿美元<ref>{{cite news|url=http://finance.yahoo.com/news/40-billion-jet-buying-spree-101537875.html|title=40 billion jet spending spree|publisher=[[Yahoo|Yahoo]]|date=2014-10-16|access-date=2016-03-19}}</ref>。2015年8月15日，靛蓝航空确认了上述订购意向，其中包括部分空中客车A321neo系列的选择权，以便服务更多乘客和更长的航线，订单总价值达到265亿美元<ref name="fleet"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/opinion/interviews/would-be-foolish-to-not-focus-on-india-says-indigo-airlines-president-aditya-ghosh/articleshow/48689889.cms|title=Would be foolish to not focus on India, says IndiGo airlines president Aditya Ghosh|access-date=2016-03-19|newspaper=The Economic Times|date=2015-08-27}}</ref>。以订购飞机数量计算，这在当时是空中客车历史上最大的单笔订单<ref name="largestit" /><ref name="largestab">{{cite press release|title=IndiGo signs MoU for 250 A320neo aircraft|url=http://www.airbus.com/newsevents/news-events-single/detail/indigo-signs-mou-for-250-a320neo-aircraft/|work=Airbus|access-date=2016-03-19|date=2014-10-15|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235908/http://www.airbus.com/newsevents/news-events-single/detail/indigo-signs-mou-for-250-a320neo-aircraft/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

