===旅客服务===

作为低成本航空公司，靛蓝航空只提供[[经济舱|经济舱]]座位，每架空中客车A320飞机设180座。为了保持低票价，靛蓝航空不提供免费餐饮，乘客可以付费购买餐食<ref>{{cite web|url=https://content.goindigo.in/Corporate/faqs|title=IndiGo FAQ's|publisher=IndiGo|access-date=2013-11-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160316052900/https://content.goindigo.in/Corporate/faqs|archivedate=2016-03-16}}</ref>。靛蓝航空不提供[[机上娱乐|机上娱乐]]系统，但是提供靛蓝航空发行的空中杂志《Hello 6E》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.livemint.com/Opinion/5DaJcaw9ivPEZE3DJHklIO/Coffee-with-6E.html|title=Coffee with 6E|newspaper=Mint|access-date=2016-03-19|date=2015-10-26|archive-date=2016-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309200833/http://www.livemint.com/Opinion/5DaJcaw9ivPEZE3DJHklIO/Coffee-with-6E.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。乘客可以支付额外费用选择靛蓝航空的“6E Xtras”服务，包括预选座位、灵活退改签、优先登机等服务<ref>{{cite web|url=https://content.goindigo.in/Corporate/landingpage11|title=IndiGo 6E Plus|publisher=IndiGo|access-date=2016-06-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126102452/https://content.goindigo.in/Corporate/landingpage11|archivedate=2015-11-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.goindigo.in/information/fees-and-charges.html?linkNav=fees-and-charges_Home-en~service-listing~1|title=Updated Fees and Charges|publisher=IndiGo|access-date=2016-06-05}}</ref>。

===标志和涂装===

靛蓝航空的标志由排成飞机形状的20个圆点组成<ref>{{cite web|url=https://content.goindigo.in/Information/IndigoExperience#page1|title=IndiGo Experience|publisher=IndiGo|access-date=2016-03-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404112124/https://content.goindigo.in/Information/IndigoExperience#page1|archivedate=2016-04-04}}</ref>。靛蓝航空使用靛蓝色和白色为主题的涂装，乘务员的制服为由时尚设计师设计的海军蓝[[丘尼卡|丘尼卡]]配帽子和靛蓝色的腰带<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.rediff.com/business/slide-show/slide-show-1-the-man-behind-indigos-amazing-success/20110208.htm|title=The man behind IndiGo's amazing success|work=Rediff|date=2011-02-08|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330195830/http://www.rediff.com/business/slide-show/slide-show-1-the-man-behind-indigos-amazing-success/20110208.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="brand">{{cite news|url=http://travel.cnn.com/mumbai/life/brand-story-behind-indigo-044435/|title=The IndiGo brand story|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2011-02-17|first=Aditi|last=Saxton|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329013803/http://travel.cnn.com/mumbai/life/brand-story-behind-indigo-044435/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

